how to enable live roload
-check if pom.xml has "spring-boot-devtools"
-Go to File > Settings > Build, Execution, Deployment > Compiler
Check Build project automatically

Go to File > Settings > Advanced Settings
Look under Compiler
Enable: “Allow auto-make to start even if application is running”